import React from 'react'; import pacific from '../../public/images/pacificdunes.jpg' import harbour from '../../public/images/harbour.jpeg' import innisbrook from '../../public/images/innisbrook.jpg' import kiawah from '../../public/images/kiawah.png' import pga from '../../public/images/pga.jpg' import pinehurst from '../../public/images/pinehurst.jpg' import scottsdale from '../../public/images/scottsdale.jpg' import torrey from '../../public/images/torrey.jpg' export const Schedule = (): JSX.Element => { const schedule = [ { course: "Pacific Dunes", blue: "6,078", white: "5,672", red: "5,158", yellow: "5,089", holes: "Back Nine", round: "Preliminary", image: pacific }, { course: "Harbour Town Golf Links", blue: "6,663", white: "6,245", red: "5,889", yellow: "4,999", holes: "Front Nine", round: "1", image: harbour }, { course: "Innisbrook", blue: "6,563", white: "6,063", red: "5,447", yellow: "4,838", holes: "Back Nine", round: "2", image: innisbrook }, { course: "TPC Scottsdale", blue: "6,612", white: "6,271", red: "5,958", yellow: "5,402", holes: "Back Nine", round: "3", image: scottsdale }, { course: "Pinehurst #2", blue: "6,907", white: "6,358", red: "5,792", yellow: "4,938", holes: "Front Nine", round: "4", image: pinehurst }, { course: "PGA National", blue: "6,735", white: "6,381", red: "6,001", yellow: "5,158", holes: "Back Nine", round: "Quarter-Finals", image: pga }, { course: "Torrey Pines", blue: "7,028", white: "6,631", red: "6,128", yellow: "5,398", holes: "Back Nine", round: "Semi-Finals", image: torrey }, { course: "Kiawah Ocean Course", blue: "6,813", white: "6,463", red: "6,157", yellow: "5,312", holes: "Back Nine", round: "Championship", image: kiawah } ] const scheduleData = schedule.map(event => { return (
{event.course}

Round: {event.round}

Holes: {event.holes}

Blue: {event.blue}

White: {event.white}

Red: {event.red}

Yellow: {event.yellow}

) }) return (
{scheduleData}
); }
